nextExpression

public Value nextExpression(java.io.PushbackReader is,
                            int radix,
                            int flags,
                            Pair anns)
                     throws java.io.IOException
Reads an s-expression from the given input port.

Parameters:
is - PushbackReader from which to read
radix - Specifies the radix of any numbers that are read
flags - Specifies attributes for the returned values (PRODUCE_IMMUTABLES, PRODUCE_ANNOTATIONS, STRICT_R5RS)
anns - additional annotations
Returns:
the read expression
Throws:
java.io.IOException - if an error occurs
